column16: Read counts were calculated using featureCounts from the SubRead package

column16: Peaks were called using MACS2 with a p-value cutoff of 1e-10 and the mfold parameter constrained between 15 and 100., To determine read depth of peaks called, bedtools coverage was used to calculate the counts
